means: compile ： 通常指根据搜集、整理的资料编辑词典或汇编文集。
edit ： 普通用词，含义广泛。指校订、编辑他人待出版的著作，也指对杂志、报刊的稿件进行编辑、编排加工。

entry.def: When you compile something such as a report, book, or programme, you produce it by collecting and putting together many pieces of information.

example.ex: Councils were required to compile a register of all adults living in their areas...
example.tran: 各地政务委员会被要求编制一份该地区成年居民的名册。

example.ex: The book took 10 years to compile...
